  <interventions>
    <interventions>Treatment: drugs - Sotagliflozin
Treatment: drugs - Placebo

Experimental: Treatment A - Sotagliflozin (fasted conditions)

Placebo Comparator: Treatment B - Placebo (fasted conditions)


Treatment: drugs: Sotagliflozin
Sotagliflozin, once daily, before the first meal of the day

Treatment: drugs: Placebo
Placebo, once daily, before the first meal of the day

</interventions>
